# The wildcard TLS cert + key for *.vistacompute1.ucmerced.edu go here and must
# NEVER be committed. Traefik mounts this dir read-only at /certs (see
# deploy/docker-compose.yml) and serves the cert via SNI (deploy/traefik/dynamic.yml).
#
# Expected filenames:
#   vistacompute1.crt   full chain (leaf + intermediates), PEM
#   vistacompute1.key   private key, PEM
*
!.gitignore
